  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Cook the onion until browned, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the red-curry-paste and cook, stirring constantly, for 1 minute.",
    "Add the binchotan charcoal powder and cook for 30 seconds.",
    "Add the coconut milk, sweet potato, and bell pepper, stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer, then reduce the heat to medium-low and cook until the sweet potato is tender, about 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in the brown sugar, tamarind paste, and sesame oil.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve hot in a Korean brass bowl."
